      "rationale": "Young's modulus (114 GPa), yield strength (880 MPa), and tangent modulus were measured from five tensile coupons from the production lot. CMM measurements of rod diameter and screw shank diameter provided geometric inputs with ±0.01 mm uncertainty. Monte Carlo propagation showed QoI uncertainty within ±3.5%, well below the 10% acceptance bound."
