      "rationale": "Eleven constructs were assembled using production-lot non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screws and 5.5 mm titanium rods. CMM verification confirmed all components within drawing tolerances. Testing was split across two accredited laboratories to characterize inter-lab variability (CV < 4%). Sample representativeness is adequate."
