      "rationale": "Testing was performed under a single ASTM F1717 configuration (10-degree offset compression-bending). No alternative loading angles or fixture variants were evaluated. This limits characterization of test condition sensitivity. Achieved level (2) is below the required level (3); this gap is noted as a limitation of the validation dataset but does not preclude acceptance given the standardized nature of the F1717 protocol."
    },
    {
