      "rationale": "A parameter mapping table was prepared cross-referencing each FEA input to the corresponding measured or specified test parameter. Geometry was taken directly from CMM measurements of the tested constructs. Boundary conditions replicate the F1717 fixture kinematics. Equivalency is fully documented."
